4 SYNOPSIS:
5 This bill would provide that when an inspection
6 is required by a local governing entity as a condition
7 of a permit for the construction, repair, or
8 maintenance of a residential or commercial swimming
9 pool, the swimming pool contractor may request the
10 local governing entity to perform the inspection.
11
12
13 A BILL
14 TO BE ENTITLED
15 AN ACT
16
17 Relating to contractors; to authorize a swimming pool
18 contractor to request any inspection required by a local
19 permit for the construction, repair, or maintenance of a
20 swimming pool, under certain conditions.
21 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
22 Section 1. When an inspection is required by a local
23 governing entity a condition of a permit for the construction,
24 repair, or maintenance of a residential or commercial swimming
25 pool, the contractor may request the local governing entity to
26 permit for the inspection if the contractor is licensed
27 pursuant to Chapter 8 of Title 34, Code of Alabama 1975 and
28 the construction, repair, or maintenance is performed by the
